Package: spef
Title: Semiparametric Estimating Functions
Version: 1.0.9
Authors@R: c(person("Sy Han (Steven)", "Chiou", email =
        "schiou@utdallas.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Xiaojing", "Wang", role = "aut"), person("Jun", "Yan",
        role = "aut"))
Description: Functions for fitting semiparametric regression models for
        panel count survival data. An overview of the package can be
        found in Wang and Yan (2011) <doi:10.1016/j.cmpb.2010.10.005>
        and Chiou et al. (2018) <doi:10.1111/insr.12271>.
